After exchanging pleasantries, we were led inside as the light of the cameras blinded us.

"Your Majesty. Welcome to Pales. It is delightful to have you here with us again."

Narrator: Instead, I was here to finalize our...

Instead, I was here to finalize our deal with Duke Reinhart -- concerning ceding our rights to Aureus, as well as to finalize our deal with Prime Minister Alvarez.

LineNo: 13593314,

Narrator: Upon our arrival to Castle Reinhart...
en


Upon our arrival to Castle Reinhart, we were greeted by the smiling faces of the Palesian and Lespian delegation as well as Duke Reinhart, who waited at the front gates.

LineNo: 13593416,

Narrator: Our convoy drove steadily across th...
en


Our convoy drove steadily across the cobbled streets of Old Town Pales. It was my second visit to Pales since becoming King of Rizia, but the atmosphere this time was way more cordial and cheerful.

Narrator: Instead, I was here to sign our dea...
en


Instead, I was here to sign our deal with Duke Reinhart as resolved by the AN -- giving us half of Aureus.

en


Instead, I was here to sign our agreement with Duke Reinhart as resolved by the AN -- giving them all the rights of Aureus. Despite our initial protests, there was nothing I could do about it now.

en


Vina was already inside, standing next to the Palesian foreign affairs team. She came to me when we entered the hall.

LineNo: 13594658,

Vina Toras: Good to see you here, Father. Glad...
en


"Good to see you here, Father. Glad you made it."

en

en

en

en

Our convoy drove steadily across the cobbled streets of Old Town Pales. It was my third visit to Pales since becoming King of Rizia, but the atmosphere this time was cordial and cheerful as opposed to my earlier visit.

Instead, I was here to sign our deal with Duke Reinhart as resolved by the AN -- giving us half of Aureus.

"Uh... I wouldn't exactly call it *dying*. But yes, thank you, Father. I did my best to support."

en

en

en


We were then led into the room where the meeting would take place.

LineNo: 13597788,

Axel Reinhart: Your Majesty. Welcome once again....
en


"Your Majesty. Welcome once again. Despite sad occurrences between our countries, it is delightful to be able to put them behind us and reach an agreement."

LineNo: 13597890,

Axel Reinhart: Today is not just about signing a...
en


"Today is not just about signing a deal, it's about laying the foundation for enduring cooperation and mutual benefit between Pales and Rizia."

LineNo: 13597992,

Axel Reinhart: With the signing of our resolution...
en


"With the signing of our resolution, we will be building a new gas pipeline between our countries. Palesian government and LesPower will be handling the costs as well as the construction."

Axel Reinhart: It is a pleasure to welcome you ag...
en


"It is a pleasure to welcome you again."

en


"Thank you, Duke Reinhart. Your words mean a lot for me and our kingdom."

en


"You are so kind, Duke Reinhart. Thank you for having us."

LineNo: 13598432,

Player_Romus: It is a pleasure to be here under...
en


"It is a pleasure to be here under such promising circumstances. This deal will mark a new chapter for both of our nations."

LineNo: 13598534,

Player_Romus: To be fair, I don't need a meeting...
en

en


He started laughing along with everyone around the table.

en

en


"I must also thank the Rizian delegates. They were instrumental in reaching an agreement."

Axel Reinhart: Uh... Fair enough!
en


"Uh... Fair enough!"

en


Vina bowed her head.

Narrator: The delegates bowed their heads.
en


The delegates bowed their heads.

LineNo: 13599526,

en


"Rizia has agreed to grant half of the claims they won to Pales -- acknowledging that our state owns 75% of the Aureus field."

en

Narrator: Instead, I was here to finalize our...
en


Instead, I was here to finalize our deal with Duke Reinhart, concerning buying the extraction rights to Aureus, as well as to inaugurate the opening of the pipeline -- which will be operational after today.

en


"I missed you, Vina. How was Pales?"

en

"Be careful, Vina. It's *Duke Reinhart* and it will stay that way."

en


"Oh God. What are you talking about?"

LineNo: 13603928,

Vina Toras: Oh come on, Father...
en


"Oh come on, Father..."

LineNo: 13604030,

LineNo: 13604132,

Vina Toras: Well, anyway...
en


"Well, anyway..."

en


"We should go to the Old Town before we leave. It's amazing how they preserved it just in the middle of the skyscrapers."

Player_Romus: Thank you. Let's just get this ove...
en


"Thank you. Let's just get this over with."

Narrator: There was a brief silence as his fa...
en


There was a brief silence as his face soured."

LineNo: 13604810,

Axel Reinhart: Well...
en


"Well..."

Axel Reinhart: Rizia has agreed to buy the sole r...

"Rizia has agreed to buy the sole rights to extract resources from the Aureus Field."

en


"It's good to see you, Your Majesty."

en


"In return, Lespia will be granting  extraction rights for one-quarter of the Aureus fields to Rizia."

The assistants placed all the necessary papers in front of us to sign.

After exchanging congratulations, we were led outside where the ceremony would take place in front of the press.

Narrator: We stood in front of a massive boar...

We stood in front of a massive board with an illustrated map of the Antacean Sea, depicting the Aureus field as a bridge that connects Pales, Rizia and Lespia.

We stood in front of a massive board with an illustrated map of the Antacean Sea, depicting the Aureus field as a bridge that connects Pales and Rizia.

The stage itself was an outlandish construct, with a towering replica of a drilling rig with a huge logo of LesPower on it, floating over a pool of water.

LineNo: 13608868,

Narrator: As soon as we stepped onto the stag...
en


As soon as we stepped onto the stage, the applause of the crowd blended with the loud music from the speakers and the sounds of pictures being taken -- overwhelming me for a few seconds.

Narrator: Made to look like a sophisticated m...
en


Made to look like a sophisticated machine with oversized dials, levers, and flashing lights, it was less a piece of industrial equipment and more a prop from a science fiction movie.

LineNo: 13609660,

Narrator: The stage itself was an outlandish...
en


The stage itself was an outlandish construct, with a colossal replica of a pipeline going right through it and a gigantic valve wheel at its center.

LineNo: 13609762,

Narrator: The valve was painted in garish col...
en


The valve was painted in garish colors and connected to a series of exaggerated, cartoonish pipes that snaked their way across the stage, complete with artificial steam vents and blinking lights.

LineNo: 13609864,

Narrator: The geysers were choreographed to e...
en


The geysers were choreographed to erupt in unison with the crescendo of the music.

Laurento Esquibel: I want to applaud you again, Your...
en


"I want to applaud you again, Your Majesty, for your decisive actions that led to a successful deal despite that violent incident."

en

As the music came to an end and the applause subsided, I took a clearer look at the crowd that was gathered.

LineNo: 13614062,

Narrator: People in their best formal attire...
en


People in their best formal attire were standing somewhat awkwardly amidst this bizarre setting. They casted amused glances at the entertainers who mingled among them - performers dressed as engineers and geologists, complete with exaggeratedly large yellow helmets.

LineNo: 13614164,

en


Duke Reinhart then took the microphone and started explaining the importance of Aureus and the deal that was finalized.

After thanking and congratulating LesPower, he introduced me and gestured at me to take the microphone.

After congratulating the delegates and thanking me, he gestured at me to take the microphone.

"...And I invite, King Romus."

"...And I invite, our partner, King Romus."

I took the microphone amidst the applause.

"Duke of Pales, my friend Axel Reinhart. I want to thank you from the bottom of my heart for reaching a mutual understanding."

"Ladies and gentlemen and dear friends. I would like to thank Duke Reinhart for inviting us to attend this grand ceremony."

"Mr. Reinhart, esteemed delegates and ladies and gentlemen..."

"Duke of Pales, my friend Axel Reinhart, as well as Prime Minister of Lespia, Mr. Alvarez. I want to thank you from the bottom of my heart for reaching a mutual understanding."

LineNo: 13616264,

Player_Romus: Today, we are taking part in a tru...
en


"Today, we are taking part in a truly signal event that testifies to the effectiveness of our countries’ cooperation in accomplishing the most ambitious projects."

LineNo: 13616366,

Player_Romus: Relations between Rizia, Pales and...
en


"Relations between Rizia, Pales and Lespia have reached a new peak. This is now being reflected in our cooperation on Aureus."

LineNo: 13616468,

Player_Romus: Despite a recent deterioration of...
en


"Despite a recent deterioration of our relations, we have come together to achieve a historic agreement -- a testament of true diplomacy and our mutual desire for cooperation."

LineNo: 13616856,

Player_Romus: Despite attempts to divide our cou...
en


"Despite attempts to divide our countries, we deliberately chose the path to peace and mutual growth for both of us."

LineNo: 13616958,

Player_Romus: Today, we have concluded a histori...
en


"Today, we have concluded a historic agreement, which is a testament of true diplomacy and our mutual desire for cooperation."

LineNo: 13617434,

Player_Romus: Relations between Rizia and Pales...
en


"Relations between Rizia and Pales have reached a new peak. This is now being reflected in our cooperation on Aureus."

Player_Romus: We are more than excited about the...
en


"We are more than excited about the massive amounts of energy it will produce."

LineNo: 13617948,

Player_Romus: Thanks to our cooperation with Pal...

"Thanks to our cooperation with Pales, Rizia will soon be transporting billions of cubic meters of natural gas."

LineNo: 13618050,

Player_Romus: I am honored to announce the offic...
en


"I am honored to announce the official agreement between our countries."

Player_Romus: Let us not forget that, despite ho...
en


"Let us not forget that, despite holding the right to claim part ownership of Aureus, we have decided to cede all of our rights to our partners in Pales."

Player_Romus: In the name of friendship and futu...
en


"In the name of friendship and future cooperation, Rizia transferred all claims of Aureus to the Grand Duchy of Pales."

LineNo: 13618356,

Player_Romus: I am honored to announce the offic...
en


"I am honored to announce the official agreement between our three countries."

LineNo: 13618848,

Player_Romus: I would like to note that extracti...
en


"I would like to note that extracting and transporting gas is no easy job as someone may think. It will be a great undertaking."

LineNo: 13618950,

en


"This project has many benefits not only for our people and our country but also for our neighbors and the region as a whole."

"Ladies and gentlemen. Believe me, I am shocked as much as every one of you."

"Ladies and gentlemen," (gesturing at the geysers) "Believe me, I am shocked as much as every one of you."

en


The crowd burst out in laughter.

"This field will hopefully have many benefits not only for Pales and its people, but also for its neighbors and the region as a whole."

"Thanks to the support and high professionalism of LesPower, the project is already implemented in a timely manner."

"Thanks to the support and high professionalism of our Palesian counterparts, new energy deals can soon be implemented in a timely manner."

en


"I am certain that in the future, Rizia and Pales will implement many more mutually beneficial joint projects, both in energy and in other fields."

en


"I must point out that we live in a volatile region, where we're seeing more indications of the situation being further aggravated. However, Rizia and Pales are showing an example to everyone."

Player_Romus: Rizia will continue its duty with...
en


"Rizia will continue its duty with finding resolutions to conflicts in our region and we will stay as one of the most reliable trading partners in Merkopa."

en


"I would like to congratulate the Palesian leadership for displaying the political courage and will to accomplish what we have today."

"Before I finish, I would like to highlight the importance of Palesian-Rizian friendship for Southern Merkopa."

en


"Before I finish, I would like to highlight the importance of Lespian-Rizian friendship in Southern Merkopa."

en


"Before I finish, I would like to highlight how important it is for the monarchies of Merkopa to stick together."

en


"I would like to bring my speech to a close..."

LineNo: 13621562,

Player_Romus: We must not forget. Major powers l...
en


"We must not forget. Major powers like us have a responsibility to the region. And today, we are showing the world that we take our duties seriously."
